{"tid":1327912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]如果因為有人被捕 需要影片黎做抗辯 我應該要點做","createTime":"2019-07-17T18:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:28:28.000Z","uid":4298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1243d4db3a47e1e92bc869a885a54f128d198942","tid":1327912,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:32:53.000Z","msg":"14號過左幾日 <br />\n我想引返起一d 事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成30幾條友俾人拉左 點解求片既人咁少既呢 <br />\n你地究竟有冇諗住幫下義士 <br />\n班狗係唔係都會提堂先 夠唔夠料 都唔會理囉<br />\n<br />\n但係我地冇係有野可以做架 <br />\n唔會令到義士覺得得自己一個對抗  冇人幫到佢 我地要俾片俾信心佢囉<br />\n<br />\n利伸 <br />\n有朋友出左事 我都想求片<br />\n但係我唔知點樣先有效 <br />\n歡迎起底"},{"pid":"145092612c134d439e48c59e0156593cf64abd1c","tid":1327912,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:33:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"3f7e83dbba8fef128cdd7fb0a8207e7a5bd786fb","tid":1327912,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"148df65386492c0b5318559985088a23935716b8","tid":1327912,"uid":229695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"I have nothing to say"},{"pid":"64b97434b95bf8fab3fd0c86390059181647ab78","tid":1327912,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:36:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"58ef783b4037656991e44e6d64967076fe0390a0","tid":1327912,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:36:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我冇野講<br />\n<code>求幫推</code>"},{"pid":"8cab784fa5b777df4e1959b10f5676a17d619b95","tid":1327912,"uid":40051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"放TG 如果有人有野就會搵到你"},{"pid":"15ebebfd97bd4bff1f89478f6841455fa2d1184b","tid":1327912,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://